{"tid":1888634,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet澀琪公開與姜河那合照 展現意外人脈","createTime":"2020-02-20T10:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T01:33:52.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"76ea281b0490af0c4e7373e1f79f7f735ce1500d","tid":1888634,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"bnt新聞訊 韓國人氣組合Red Velvet成員澀琪公開了與演員姜河那的合照。<br />\n<br />\n19日，澀琪通過個人Instagram上傳了與演員姜河那的合照和&ldquo;幻想童話&rdquo;的簡短文字。照片中，澀琪和姜河那擺出親密V型姿勢，露出微笑，特別是姜河那的&ldquo;禮儀手&rdquo;也格外引人注目。而網友們對兩人意外的人脈感到好奇和意外。<br />\n<br />\n另外，姜河那目前正在出演話劇「幻想童話」，而澀琪所屬的Red Velvet於去年12月發表了新曲「Psycho」深受大眾喜愛。Phoebe/文 澀琪INS/圖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/red-velvet%E6%BE%80%E7%90%AA%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%88%87%E5%A7%9C%E6%B2%B3%E9%82%A3%E5%90%88%E7%85%A7-%E5%B1%95%E7%8F%BE%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%88-091420375.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2Fred-velvet%25E6%25BE%2580%25E7%2590%25AA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A7%259C%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E9%2582%25A3%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2585%25A7-%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2584%2588-091420375.html&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=b5928f0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/red-velvet%E6%BE%80%E7%90%AA%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%88%87%E5%A7%9C%E6%B2%B3%E9%82%A3%E5%90%88%E7%85%A7-%E5%B1%95%E7%8F%BE%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%88-091420375.html</a>"},{"pid":"8585f20be15eba38d2bf43e6b97daaef27b1d693","tid":1888634,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/38t0.GDvENEFXEVn4YgM9g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTIwO2g9NDQyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/ko_KR/News/bntnews.cn/9gxcf5p3cjuj792sq40wsa2nyp5nz3ly.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fn